z">斯特兰兹</a><br />Jocewavy<br />肯尼·阿尔斯塔尔（Kenny Allstar）<br /> Seani b</p><p> <strong>7 月 14 日，星期日</strong><br />多哈猫<br />唐·托利弗（Don Toliver）<br />雷马<br />泰拉<br /><a href="/artists/digga-d">d</a><br />华夫叔叔<br /><a href="/artists/ruger">鲁格</a><br />泰佐达阵<br />里奇·阿米里（Rich Amiri）<br /> Nemzzz<br />纳迪亚·杰（Nadia Jae）<br /> Snoochie害羞</p><figure id="attachment_3467878" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3467878" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3467878" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty.jpg" alt="冰香料和粉红色" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/pinkpantheress-and-Ice-Spice-getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3467878" class="wp-caption-text">无线2023的冰香料和粉红色的粉红色和粉红色</figcaption></figure><p>Wireless去年宣布，在大流行之后，他们将在2021年将标志性的节日搬到水晶宫公园后，将搬到Finsbury Park。</p><p>音乐节安排在Hyde Park，Harewood House和伊丽莎白女王奥林匹克公园等场所举行。但是，在与无线的发起人节共和国签署了为期五年的合同之后，这发生了变化。此举是为了增加伦敦北部的“巨额收入”，并促进当地经济。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/wireless-festival-announces-first-names-for-2023-including-travis-scott-and-50-cent-3386503">去年的无线音乐节于2023年7月在Finsbury Park举行</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">特拉维斯·斯科特（Travis Scott）</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/playboi-carti">Playboi Carti</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/d-block-europe">D-Block Euro