aster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fleeds-festival-tickets%2Fartist%2F35438" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里（利兹）</a> 。</p><p> Del Rey和Fred再次。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2021-3031483">cat鱼在2021年的谣言中最后一条出现</a>，然后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/catfish-and-the-bottlemen-bondy-says-he-left-the-band-last-year-3240536">吉他手约翰尼·“邦迪”·邦德（Johnny“ Bondy” Bond）证实他已经离开了乐队</a>。</p><p>同时，加拉格尔（Gallagher）将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">跟随他的英国和爱尔兰巡回演唱会，</a>通过完整播放专辑来<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-oasis-definitely-maybe-30th-anniversary-uk-tour-dates-tickets-3515369">庆祝Oasis“肯定</a>”。</p><p>在其他新闻中，Flo最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/flo-share-sensual-new-single-walk-like-this-3600165">分享了他们感性的新单曲“像这样”</a> ，标志着他们本年度的首次发行。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/teddy-swims-cover-taylor-swift-cruel-summer-watch-3569448">泰迪电台1的<em>Live Lounge</em>出现了泰迪游泳，并带有泰勒·斯威夫特（Taylor Swift）的“残酷夏天”的封面</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/teddy-swims-kid-kapichi-and-more-lead-30-new-names-for-reading-leeds-2024-3616638">泰迪邮报游泳，Kid Kapichi和更多领先的30个新名称，用于Reading＆Leeds 2024，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
